<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Tuft" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Tuft,</orth> cluster, clump: <cit><quote>at the t. of olives,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.5.75" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 5, 75</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>behind the t. of pines,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 34</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>by yon t. of trees,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 2.3.53" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 3, 53</bibl></cit>. In <bibl n="shak. lll 4.2.90" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 2, 90</bibl> O. Edd. <emph>turf.</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>